For all who facing trouble registering the software , if you have a previous version of Winrar then replaced it with this version you will face "40 days trial" problem like I had myself . to solve this :

1- Uninstall any previous ver of Winrar
2- Install this ver
3- Open the winrar
4- Create a "rarreg.key" file and put "0" in it and save it //without "" of-course
5- Drag n drop this file to the Winrar program window to remove any previous keys 
6- Drag n drop the "rarreg.key" file comes with this torrent in the same previous way to register your key 

enjoy

and for the record , you may skip steps 4,5 and do step 6 at once , but I prefer the clean way :-)
